179
00:13:42,047 --> 00:13:43,916
Obrigado, senhor.

180
00:13:44,052 --> 00:13:46,055
Agradeço-lhe imenso.

181
00:13:49,321 --> 00:13:51,357
Posso ser sincero, Mr. Tucker?

182
