- Parabéns.

1250
01:33:47,093 --> 01:33:48,093
Obrigada.

1251
01:33:50,589 --> 01:33:51,806
Felicidades, papá.

1252
01:33:53,855 --> 01:33:55,288
<i>Gracias</i>, Juan.

1253
01:33:56,958 --> 01:33:58,863
